author: The Critical Drinker
description:
In not-so-shocking news, a new article by Forbes reveals that Marvel has lost 60% of its pre-Endgame audience, Chris Evans was hailed as a "washed up moviestar" in a recent press junket, and the ongoing tragedy of Alien Earth winds towards its ridiculous conclusion. Join me, MauLer, Ryan Kinel, The Movie Cynic and Heelvsbabyface for Open Bar 157.

title: Open Bar #157 - Marvel Loses Half Its Audience, Alien Earth Disaster, Chris Evans Blasted
